short.ta: நீங்கள் கார்ட்டூன் கேம்களை விரும்புகிறீர்களா? ஸ்கூபி-டூ மற்றும் ஷாகியுடன் சாண்ட்விச் ஸ்டாக் ஆர்கேட் கேமை விளையாடுங்கள்!
short.te: మీకు కార్టూన్ గేమ్‌లు ఇష్టమా? స్కూబీ-డూ మరియు షాగీతో శాండ్‌విచ్ స్టాక్ ఆర్కేడ్ గేమ్ ఆడండి!
short.th: คุณชอบเกมการ์ตูนหรือไม่? เล่นเกมอาร์เคด Sandwich Stack กับ Scooby-Doo และ Shaggy!
short.tr: Çizgi film oyunlarını sever misin? Scooby-Doo ve Shaggy ile Sandwich Stack arcade oyununu oynayın!
short.uk: Вам подобаються мультики? Грайте в аркадну гру Sandwich Stack зі Скубі-Ду та Шеггі!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,:
Play the Sandwich Stack arcade game with Scooby-Doo and Shaggy! Their fridge has exploded, and now you can help them now to catch as many ingredients as you can!

Move Scooby and Shaggy left and right to collect the falling ingredients. Build a sandwich of your own creation or open the recipe book and construct a classic (for extra points). Watch out for bombs or it will be game over.

To make things more fun, the two friends have decided to pile the falling ingredients onto slices of bread and make sandwiches out of them! Don't let the food fall onto the floor and waste and catch it quickly!

How To Play :
- use A and D to move

To swipe Install this extension to play the Scooby Doo Snadwich Stack or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
